rep.scrame.model

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • rep.scrame.model.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that defines a course. This class stores and manages information regarding enrolled students, students in waitlist, course grading policy, lecturers, and course sessions.
